Kameleon recipe and steps for making a cigri-devel appliance
============================================================

Warning: kameleon version >= 1.2.2 required

Run `kameleon debian_cigri_devel` from this directory or for better customization:

- cp recipes/debian_cigri_devel.yaml /var/lib/kameleon/recipes/my_debian_cigri_devel.yaml
- vi /var/lib/kameleon/recipes/my_debian_cigri_devel.yaml
- kameleon my_debian_cigri_devel

